        <h2>Supporting Aspiring Managers</h2>
        <p>Transitioning into a Registered Manager role is one of the steepest learning curves in healthcare. My mentorship program is designed to bridge the gap between "doing the job" and "mastering the regulation."</p>
        
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="mentor-card">
                <h3>New Manager Fast-Track</h3>
                <p>A 12-week intensive remote program covering the essentials of the Single Assessment Framework, safe staffing, and effective auditing.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mentor-card">
                <h3>CQC Interview Prep</h3>
                <p>Mock "Fit Person" interviews conducted via video link. We build your confidence and ensure you can articulate your service's vision to inspectors.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mentor-card">
                <h3>Aspiring RM Mentoring</h3>
                <p>For Deputy Managers or Seniors looking to step up. We focus on leadership mindset, governance, and managing 'Requires Improvement' turnarounds.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">
            <a href="index.html#contact" class="btn">Book a Discovery Call</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-box">
        <h2>Why Mentorship Matters</h2>
        <p>Regulation is complex, but leadership shouldn't be lonely. Having a mentor who has <strong>owned care businesses and been a Registered Manager</strong> means you get practical, "real-world" advice that textbooks can't provide.</p>
